title: Ep 33: We’re Millennials feat. Jennica Thompson
itunes:title: Ep 33: We’re Millennials feat. Jennica Thompson
description: We’re back this week with another one of Shannon’s closest friends and YouTube superstar, Jennica Thompson. From her journey as a teen mom to her current role as a hot mom, Jennica talks about the climb to where she is now. The girls talk about being millennials and OG Facebook photo dumps. Why does Jennica know so much about caskets? How does she feel about co-parenting? What is up with her colon? Shannon asks Jennica about her fabulous style and they recap her 30th birthday in Cabo, and they even chat about their beef from Very Cavallari, all in episode 33.
